high_descs: Turn around and go to the stove.
Pick up the pot on the stove.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Put the pot in the refrigerator then take the pot out of the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the stove.
Put the pot on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled pot on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around to your left walk straight, then head to the stove
Pick up the pot  on the stove
Turn around to your right and head to the fridge then open the fridge
Put the pot inside the fridge beside the apple then close and open the fridge
Turn to your left and head back to the stove
Put the pot to the stove
anns.task_desc: Put the pot in out the fridge going back to the stove.

high_descs: Turn around, then turn right at the kitchen island, then turn left to face the stove.
Pick up the pot on the stove.
Go around the kitchen island and then turn left at the fridge.
Chill the pot inside of the fridge.
Turn left to return to the stove.
Place the pot on the stove, on the front right range.
anns.task_desc: Put a chill pot on the stove.

high_descs: turn around towards the shelf and then turn right and locate the gas cooker
pick up the pot
turn right and locate the fridge
place the pot in the fridge for some time to cool
turn left towards the gas cooker
place the pot on the gas cooker
anns.task_desc: place a cold pot on the gas cooker

high_descs: Turn around and go straight. Then turn right and left to find the stove.
Pick up the pan front the front burner of the stove.
Carry the pan to the right around the island to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the pot inside. Shut the door. Open the fridge and take the pan back out and shut the door.
Carry the pan to the left, and back to the stove.
Place the pan on the front right burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pan and replace it to the stove.

high_descs: Turn right, then go left just before the bar. Turn right at the end of the bar, then face the stove on your left.
Pick up the silver pot on the stove.
Turn around and walk to the end of the bar, then face the refrigerator on your left.
Put the pot in the refrigerator, leave it for a few minutes, then take it out.
Turn around and walk back to the stove.
Put the silver pot on front right eye of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pot on the stove.
